sequenceDiagram
  participant U as user
  participant H as Harness
  participant M as Model
  participant T as ToolRuntime
  participant W as workspace

  U->>H: Fix failed tests
  H->>M: Build messages
  M-->>H: propose edit intent
  H->>T: Execute after permission is passed
  T->>W: Modify files
  Note over H,T: Process crashes or interrupts
  H-->>H: Only restore from messages
  H-->>W: Unable to confirm side effect boundaries
